flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B[User runs CLI command]
    B --> C[CLI parses arguments]
    C --> D[Runner.run_all test_dir]

    D --> E[TestDiscovery discovers test files]
    E --> F{Any tests found?}

    F -- No --> G[Print no tests found]
    G --> Z([End])

    F -- Yes --> H[Create ExecutionRequest list]
    H --> I[ParallelExecutor executes requests]

    I --> J[Each request runs through PytestBackend]
    J --> K[Collect ExecutionResult list]

    K --> L[ResultAggregator creates Summary]
    L --> M[AnalyticsReporter prints analytics]

    M --> N{Any failed tests?}
    N -- Yes --> O[Print failed test details]
    N -- No --> P[Print all tests passed]

    O --> Z([End])
    P --> Z([End])
